items.title: ServiceNow Discloses Artificial Intelligence Financial Target For 2026
items.description: The rise of "agentic" AI has yet to boost ServiceNow stock or most software makers as monetization ramps slowly. ServiceNow disclosed a new AI financial target Monday.
